categories: Category:Cut content from Star Wars: The Old Republic

nodes.text: Setali Dexsoreco was a female Human captain of the Death's Claw pirate gang living during the Galactic War. In 3636 BBY she and her crew were on Ziost when the former Sith Emperor Vitiate came to the world and possessed many of the Imperials on the planet, turning them into his puppets to murder civilians.
Setali Dexsoreco appears in the game files for Star Wars: The Old Republic under npc.daily_area.ziost.mob.part04 category. She does not appear in the live version of the game.
